<h2>Before filing</h2>
<ul>
  <li>Check the claimant and defendant names and addresses.</li>
  <li>Check the Particulars of Claim and Schedule of Loss match the facts and figures.</li>
  <li>Attach copies of the evidence listed in the Evidence Index when required.</li>
  <li>Check whether enough time has been given after the pre-action demand.</li>
  <li>Check the current HMCTS court fee before paying the court.</li>
</ul>

<h2>Official form</h2>
<p>
  The pack includes a completed official Form N1. Review it carefully before filing. The N1 is populated
  from the answers provided in the claims interview.
</p>

<h2>Filing route</h2>
<p>
  England money claims may be issued online where suitable or by using the paper N1 route. Follow the
  court's current instructions and keep proof of filing and payment.
</p>
